I want to work in tech because I love building meaningful solutions. For me, programming is not just about code; it’s about understanding problems, designing efficient systems, and creating tools that make people’s lives easier. The continuous learning, fast-paced innovation, and opportunity to make an impact are what keep me motivated to grow in this field.


